profile:
Hire A Maid has been proudly cleaning homes across the GTA since 2008, and has locally-based offices that serve West Toronto, Etobicoke, Downtown, North York, East Toronto, York Region and Durham Region.

Hire A Maid makes it easier for you to enjoy what matters most in life by freeing you of the countless hours spent cleaning your home.

Hire A Maid provides consistently superior quality house cleaning tailored to your needs. Each cleaning is performed according to our comprehensive quality checklist and your customized cleaning requirements. We actively seek out and act on your feedback to ensure your complete satisfaction with our work.

Our staff are professionally trained, carefully screened, bonded, covered by WSIB and liability insured.

To prevent cross-contamination between homes and enable you to use your preferred products, we use your cleaning equipment and supplies. Our work is 100% satisfaction guaranteed!

Service Area: 
Toronto - Downtown Toronto, North York, and Etobicoke
York Region - Markham, Richmond Hill, Vaughan
Durham Region - Pickering, Ajax, Whitby, Brooklin, Port Perry, Uxbridge, Oshawa, Courtice, Bowmanville, Clarington

Contact Information:
Toronto and York Region: (416) 463-6243
Durham Region: (905) 668-4243

Our History:
Hire A Maid was founded in 2008 by Carol Dinn in Whitby, Ontario. Since its inception, Hire A Maid has performed more than 80,000 house cleanings and thousands of deep cleanings. Prior to creating Hire A Maid, Carol held the position of Director, Fixed Term Investment Products for CIBC and before this, she managed heating and cooling services and plans for Enbridge Home Services. 

Carol’s 10-plus years of experience managing and launching successful products for large corporations and her own experience as a user of house cleaning services before founding Hire A Maid have given her company a leg up in the cleaning industry. Her extensive experience in managing and motivating staff, her highly organized approach and her customer service orientation have proven to be key ingredients in Hire A Maid's rapid success. 

Carol is passionate about house cleaning and the difference her staff make in their clients' lives. "We're not just cleaning homes; we're freeing our clients of the countless hours spent on housework (or stressing about it!).  It gives our clients more time to enjoy with family, friends or simply relaxing. And, it gives us a wonderful feeling of satisfaction knowing that we can make a big difference by giving our clients more time and less stress."

What differentiates Hire A Maid from other maid services is:

•	A high level of professionalism. We’ve been told many times by clients that our office and cleaning staff are very professional. For many homeowners, entrusting their home to a house cleaner (someone they don’t know) is a big deal. At Hire A Maid, we want our clients to feel comfortable that they have chosen a company that is well-organized, customer service oriented and that will do its best to meet their needs and to protect their interests. Hire A Maid also has general liability insurance, pays into Workers’ Compensation Insurance and remits all government taxes. – Operating honestly and ethically is the foundation of our company. 

•	A focus on hiring and retaining excellent employees. All of our new employees undergo a comprehensive training program that is followed up with ongoing support to provide them the knowledge and skills to be effective at their jobs. We strive for high employee satisfaction and believe that this leads to a culture where our staff go the extra mile for our clients.  Our excellent employee retention record also allows us to provide our clients with the consistency of having the same maids every visit.

•	Performing “the details” on every cleaning truly is Hire A Maid’s specialty.

•	We actively seek out your feedback and we guarantee our work. We want you to be absolutely satisfied with our work and we invite you to complete our quality feedback survey after every visit to tell us how we’re doing. If there is ever anything you want done differently to better ensure your satisfaction, please don’t hesitate to let us know! We value your feedback and will promptly address any concerns.

profile:
Detailed Maids is a cleaning company that focuses on Details, Quality, Consistency, Efficiency, Reliability and Honesty.


The company was founded in January 2017 by a lady who has had many years of cleaning experience working for high-end cleaning corporations as Quality Assurance Manager and Customer Service Representative.

So, after numerous years of experience she decided to take all her knowledge and create a company that has both HIGH-END QUALITY CLEANING SERVICE and VERY KNOWLEDGEABLE CUSTOMER SERVICE REPRESENTATIVES. 

So, when you call Detailed Maids, you are able to speak to someone who did the cleaning themselves and who understands your need and concerns. Someone who has the expertise to answer all you questions. Why is that important? Because we want to help you save time instead of spending more time searching and testing out other companies. 

Get everything you need by calling only one cleaning company -> Detailed Maids.
 
What makes us different?
1) CUSTOMIZED CLEANING PLAN - cleaning plan that is tailored according to your cleaning needs
2) VACUUM WITH HEPA FILTERS - Our commercial grade vacuum with HEPA filters help us not only clean your floors but the air in your home as well. Reducing the number of harmful airborne particles helps you and your family breathe easily.
3) ECO-FRIENDLY CLEANING PRODUCTS - We love to clean your home without harming your health and the environment, but at the same time we want to leave your home spotless. That is why we went above and beyond to find the best of both worlds. Our cleaning products are 100% eco-friendly which makes them safe for you, your family and your pets.
4) COLOR CODED SYSTEM - We use color coded cleaning system which reduces bacteria cross-contamination between high and low-risk areas creating a healthier and more sanitary environment. That way you can be 100% confident that the cloths from your bathroom will never touch your kitchen counter tops.
5) NO CONTRACTS OR SERVICE AGREEMENTS - All of our clients have the right to cancel our services at any time, change cleaning frequency and reschedule their appointments as many times as they wish. That is how confident we are about our service.
6) NO HIDDEN FEES - The quote you receive over the phone or email is what you will be paying. No surprising charges on your credit card.


WHY DETAILED MAIDS?
-We clean your home top to bottom, left to right. We do it all. As simple as that.
Call us today to book your home cleaning.

profile:
Our company has been consistently recognized by many of our clients as one of the most reliable companies they have come across. We take great pride in that and look forward to maintaining our reputation.

Military Maintenance and Military Maid was founded on the principles of reliability, quality workmanship, and fair pricing. We pride ourselves on helping our customers complete their projects on time and within budget.

The Military Maintenance branch includes carpenters, plumbers, electricians, painters and professional handyman to complete any project you have in mind. We Work Closely with Our team to get best results.

The Military Maid branch of our team handles all the heavy duty cleaning services required at homes and offices. We can clean anything with no job being too big for our team, we’ve seen it all. 



MILITARY MAID

Our team of dedicated professionals will treat your home like their own. We will always provide our honest and professional opinion to ensure you get the best advice for your home.
Our in-house team of professionals can handle all tasks from large scale renovations to down to the smallest repairs. What does this mean? It means you get the highest quality of work without paying the large markup fees associated when work is subcontracted out. Our hands approach ensures a high level of quality is maintained and pricing is what it should be?
Did you know? Some companies simply outsource the majority of their jobs and markup the pricing anywhere from 25% to 80%! That means you could be drastically overpaying for work by thousands of dollars. Our pricing is based on a simple and fair formula of time and materials. We don’t overcharge simply because you own a nice house.
Choose us and know that our dedicated team will take care of you from start to finish and you will be paying a competitive industry price.

Now more than ever cleaners are taking every precaution while deep cleaning. From wearing gloves, shoe covers and masks to disinfecting vacuums between appointments and using hand sanitizer frequently. 

A deep clean means finding all the little spots, adding hours to a traditional cleaning, this is where we clean over and under every surface giving your home the Ultimate Clean! It doesn't stop there, the cleaning is only half the job. The CDC recommends spraying surfaces with a household bleach or a household cleaner with at least 70% alcohol. This will kill those germs that can cause viral respiratory illness. 

So with a deep clean and a disinfectant your home will be sparkling by the time we're finished!

Stand out above the rest when you choose our team to clean your office or home.

profile:
KEEP’N IT KLEAN offers a hassle free way to clean your home.  We are reliable, consistent, thorough, professional and we treat your home with tender loving care.

What does KEEP’N IT KLEAN service include?
Our services can be specialized to meet your individual needs.  We offer standard and deep cleans, one time or on-going regular service.  

Our standard clean includes:
•	Cleaning of all kitchen surfaces including cupboard fronts, counter tops, appliances, sinks and floors
•	Cleaning of all bathroom surfaces including tub, tiles, shower, sink, vanity, mirrors, toilet and floors
•	Vacuuming of carpets and floors throughout.  Steam clean tile, laminate, wood floors
•	Dusting of furniture, pictures, window sills, baseboards, light fixtures, garbage removal

Our deep clean includes all the benefits of a standard clean PLUS:
•	Washing baseboards, interior doors/frames/knobs, 
•	Wiping down/dusting inside of kitchen & bathrooms cupboards, wiping down inside of appliances
•	Interior window cleaning (where reachable), vacuum furniture

How often will KEEP’N IT KLEAN clean my home?
Monday to Friday, on a regular on-going basis (weekly, bi-weekly, monthly) or for that one-time special occasion when you need extra help.  We can also help you with you moving in/moving out cleaning.

Who will clean my home?
A team of two will arrive at your home ready to tackle your cleaning needs with all supplies (mostly eco-friendly).  We are bonded and insured so that you have peace of mind knowing you can trust us.

How much does KEEP’N IT KLEAN service cost?
Every home and person’s cleaning needs are different.  Contact us and we will provide you with a hassle free, no obligation quote.
